              "free_text": [
                " Stacked-foil experiment. A simple",
                "chemical procedure yields a carrier-free Mg28",
                "solution free from Al+3 ion and Na24 activity. The",
                "procedure is based on the fact that carrier-free Mg",
                "will form a radiocolloid in basic solution and will",
                "be held up on a glass frit."
